<br />
**Methods**:

-   **component(path : String)**<br />
    Returns the component with the given path. If there is no such component
    in the webmiddle, then the function is called recursively on the
    parent, if any.

-   **registerComponent(path, Component)<br />
    **Allows to add a component to a webmiddle, this is mainly used
    internally at construction time, but can also be used to add a
    component at a later time.

-   **log(…args)<br />
    **Utility logging function, the args are printed to the console. The
    log is skipped if the “verbose” setting is not true.

